General.Name: Ellwee AB
General.Description: Ellwee Ab (Publ) develops, manufactures, and sells four-wheel electric vehicles in Sweden. It primarily focuses on ease of movement within the urban and confined areas/communities, and the golf segment and gated communities. The company offers cooler ASM, multi fixation rear, hitch bracket for pin, cup holder, quick release locking, sand jar, protective cover, storage box helmet, golfbag fixation, E-rack, side view mirror, saddle cover, fixation knob, handle bar fixation with knob, battery charger, fixation tough claw, tablet fixation, umbrella holder ASM, mobile phone holder, and hitch bracket with tow bar. Ellwee Ab (Publ) was founded in 2015 and is based in Trollhättan, Sweden.
